    • validateTone

      public int validateTone(int bits)
      Checks if CapTone is true for all units specified by bits.
      Parameter:
      bits - Bit mask specifying all units to be checked.
      Gibt zurück:
      Bit mask, 1 for every requested unit where CapTone is false.
